Package ncochran.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DecisionLinesEvent
    This class holds all of the information required for a Decision Lines Event.
    Edge
    A horizontal Edge is used to transition between vertical Lines and contains a height, a leftLine, and a rightLine.
    Line
    The Line class contains a choice, a horizontal position, and the edges associated with this Line and is used to determine the rankings of the Choices.
    TestDecisionLinesEvent
    This class is used to test the DecisionLinesEvent.
    TestEdge
    This class is used to test the Edge entity.
    TestLine
    This class is used to test the Line entity.
